reviewText: Pictures are very dark. Nice models, nice circumstances but final impression - damaged by poor filming.  I would recommend to do this same film once again ( but models got older :-(  )

Too boring for my taste.  Yes, there's lots of male nudity, but ....  You know how nudists say that there's nothing sexy about their gatherings?  That's how this film was shot.  You'll see naked guys hiking, playing in the water, posing for pictures, but it's all SO platonic and innocent, I just couldn't get into it.  I didn't find the guys all that hot, and there weren't enough closeup shots.
This movie is great for anyone who is interested in the beauty of the male form.  It's a hot behind the scenes video look of a popular male nude photobook.
